{"tid":2357473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［傳真社］龍門張俊傑仍與富臨集團有關人士共同持有公司","createTime":"2021-01-07T12:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T12:46:24.000Z","uid":9116,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"709ee037b61a7397d3f2deca9d12db5dec54e199","tid":2357473,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:28:09.000Z","msg":"【龍門爭議】香港政治環境催生了「黃藍經濟圈」，意指透過光顧政見相近的商家令該陣營壯大，但亦出現一些爭議。傳真社過去半年收到近10宗投訴，指「黃店」龍門冰室處理「捐款」用途與聲稱不符，包括去年初開展16個項目收入高達2,300多萬元，但最後倒蝕過百萬元，質疑負責人張俊傑處理帳目有問題，希望傳真社介入調查。基於公眾利益，記者嘗試比對各項帳目及張俊傑對外聲稱是否屬實，並將資料整理公開，由大眾自行判斷。<br />\n<br />\n投訴另一主要內容是質疑龍門與「藍店」富臨有利益關係，張俊傑曾為雙方早年的合作解畫，稱2019年9月已「不收分文」出售與富臨有關的龍門股份，損失60萬元。富臨亦回應本社時指集團與龍門並無關聯。不過公司註冊處最新年報紀錄顯示，張俊傑仍與一名富臨關連人士共同持有一間公司，該公司曾為龍門冰室簽訂租約。<br />\n<br />\n傳真社透過電話、Whatsapp、Facebook、電郵及到冰室接觸張俊傑，向他提供相關資料希望他回應以釋除公眾疑慮，他均拒絕接受訪問及提供資料。<br />\n<br />\n足本報道：<br />\n龍門老闆曾稱賣股份割蓆  公司註冊顯示仍與富臨關連人士持有公司<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bnBaql\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bnBaql&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=059c99fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3bnBaql</a><br />\n龍門開16項目籌基金收入2千多萬  最終倒蝕百萬被質疑賬目不清<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XkZFfi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XkZFfi&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=601364b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XkZFfi</a><br />\n英文版本：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Xgx2jB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Xgx2jB&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=f617beb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Xgx2jB</a><br />\n<br />\n加入訂閱，撐起真相：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/backus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fbackus%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=be89ef1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/backus/</a><br />\n報料：Whatsapp/Telegram 9639 7479<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xc3AnqE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXc3AnqE.jpg&h=cf2fdae4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3136102bd8e1d4e2c1bc1250bba006ecc26a6580","tid":2357473,"uid":364651,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:29:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d5c966ff86a1379e273f17f40ab914b9b8c5336","tid":2357473,"uid":315372,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"傳真社係渣狗五毛PR"},{"pid":"1642c8c38375c710a3c8ea494be8b9d78965c709","tid":2357473,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"fake news 拉 估唔到傳真社都係deep state<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a0ef9ddf9c42cc52b9426dedd046766431e02c","tid":2357473,"uid":57797,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"哈 渣哥又開始老屈"},{"pid":"24dace6cb73bea67277858050d45f922e3e88582","tid":2357473,"uid":39221,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:30:49.000Z","msg":"留名等睇UST南亞仔狗衝入黎"},{"pid":"b2ebe39d0bfe05a9e86aeb92e96f66141b691317","tid":2357473,"uid":35125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"連登仔要批鬥傳真社了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327ccbca46e48b7a1f9d5132eb58eb9c771e2b1a","tid":2357473,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:32:16.000Z","msg":"即係富臨撐黃店?"},{"pid":"8767b461e4716a278cc93178829c3cf45bdd198f","tid":2357473,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2ebe39d0bfe05a9e86aeb92e96f66141b691317","tid":2357473,"uid":35125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"連登仔要批鬥傳真社了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T12:32:40.000Z","msg":"分化我地龍門 一定係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"h